original: Björkman, Kerstin Matilda Sofia Julia, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 4/4/91 i Gbg av arkit. Emil Billing o. Ida Maria von Wowern. G. 16 m. tandl. Fridolf Björkman. Barn: Margit f. 21, Inger 25. — Stud :ex. v. Gbgs gymn. f. fl. 11, tandl :kand. 13, tandl. 15. Tjg. v. Gbgs folksk. tandpoliklinik 15-18.
translated: Björkman, Kerstin Matilda Sofia Julia, dentist, Gothenburg, born on April 4th, 1891 in Gothenburg to architect Emil Billing and Ida Maria von Wowern. Married to dentist Fridolf Björkman in 1916. Children: Margit (born) in 1921, Inger (born) in 1925. She passed her final exams at Gothenburg gymnasium and went on to study dentistry, graduate in 1913 and become a dentist in 1915. Worked at the Gothenburg public school dental clinic from 1915 to 1918.
